BC Google Sitemapsextension README

What is the BC Google Sitemapsextension?
================================

BC Google Sitemapsis a true eZ Publish extension
that provides cronjob parts, amd class methods
to create an XML sitemap of an eZ Publish
website installation for the Google webmaster tools
and other services using a cronjob.


BC Google Sitemaps Version
==========================

The current version of BC Google Sitemapsis 1.1.3
Last Major update: September 9, 2014

You can find details about changes for this
version in doc/changelogs/CHANGELOG-1.1.3


