Requirements
============

The following requirements exists for using BC Google Sitemaps extension:

o  eZ Publish version:

   Make sure you use eZ Publish version 5.x (required) or higher. eZ Publish 5.3.x+ (Community Build, 2014.07+) is recommended.

o  PHP version:

   Make sure you have PHP 5.x or higher.

o  Google webmaster tools:

   You will require a google webmaster tools account to register the sitemap with Google.

   https://www.google.com/webmasters/tools/


Education
=========

For more information on sitemaps please review: http://www.sitemaps.org


Installation of cronjob based static sitemap generator
======================================================

- Install and activate the extension
- Test the extension via command line
- Set up the crontab to run the cronjob automatically
- Verify the sitemap was generated correctly
- Add sitemap file to your mod_rewrite rules:  RewriteRule ^/sitemap\.xml - [L]
- Add the site map using the Google Webmaster tools

Details on installing BC Google Sitemaps located in the file doc/INSTALL.


Installation of dynamic realtime sitemap generator
==================================================

- Install and activate the extension
- Test the extension via browser, http://example.com/googlesitemapdynamic/sitemap/2
- Verify the sitemap was generated correctly
- Add the sitemap using the Google Webmaster tools, https://www.google.com/webmasters/sitemaps/

Details on installing BC Google Sitemaps located in the file doc/INSTALL.


